owl:Ontology.dc:description: The IATA ONE Record vocabulary, described using W3C RDF Schema and the Web Ontology Language.
owl:Ontology.dc:title: IATA ONE Record API vocabulary

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: List of change requests that were sent as PATCH on for a Logitstics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: auditTrail:changeRequests

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Initial content of the Logistics Object at the creation moment
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: auditTrail:create

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: PATCH body of a change request sent for a specific Logistics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: changeRequests:changeRequest

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: List of mementos of a Logistics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: mementoList:mementoEntry

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: List of mementos of a Logistics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: mementos:list

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: List of operations to apply as PATCH on a Logistics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: patchRequest:operations

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: List of mementos of a Logistics Object
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: timemap:mementos

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Logistics Object Reference for which the audit trail applies
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: auditTrail:logisticsObjectRef

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: changeRequests:companyId

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: changeRequests:timestamp

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Company Id, for example airline code.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: companyInformation:companyId

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Endpoint of the company in the Internet of Logistics
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: companyInformation:serverEndpoint

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: companyInformation:supportedContentTypes

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Supported logistics object types on the server
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: companyInformation:supportedLogisticsObjects

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: delegationRequest:action

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: delegationRequest:operations

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Party that receives the delegated rights
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: delegationRequest:targetCompany

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Identifier of the logistics object to which the access is requested
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: delegationRequest:targetLogisticsObject

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Field of the object for which the error applies
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: details:attribute

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Error code
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: details:code

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Message of the error
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: details:message

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: details:resource

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: error:title

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Date and time of the memento creation
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: memento:created

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Name of the memento creator
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: memento:createdBy

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Label of the memento
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: memento:label

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: First version of the Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: memento:original

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Creation date of the memento
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: mementoEntry:datetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Non mandatory label of the memento
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: mementoEntry:label

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Link to the memento
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: mementoEntry:memento

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: First memento of the Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: mementos:firstMemento

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Last memento of the Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: mementos:lastMemento

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: OBJECT_CREATED or OBJECT_UPDATED
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: notification:eventType

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Logistics Object reference for which the notification is sent
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: notification:logisticsObjectRef

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Type of Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: notification:topic

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Operation objects must have exactly one op (operation) member; this value indicates which operation is to be performed. The value must be one of add or del; all other values result in an error
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: operation:op

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Operations objects must have exactly one p, predicate, member. The value of this member must be an IRI
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: operation:p

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Data type of the field to update
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: operationObject:datatype

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Value to update
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: operationObject:value

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Reason for the change (optional)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: patchRequest:description

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference of the Logistics Object to which te change request is applied to
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: patchRequest:logisticsObjectRef

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The company identifier of the entity that is requesting the change request
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: patchRequest:requestorCompanyIdentifier

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Revision number of the Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: patchRequest:revision

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Duration of the period to cache the subscription information in seconds
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:cacheFor

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Callback URL of the Client Subscription API where the subscriber receives Logistics Objects
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:callbackUrl

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Content type that the subscriber wants to receive in the notifications
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:contentType

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The company identifier from the Internet of Logistics of my company.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:myCompanyIdentifier

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Either a secret or API Key that ensures that only companies with this subscription information can POST to the subscriber callback endpoint
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:secret

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Flag specifying if the publisher should send the whole logistics object or not in the notification object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:sendLogisticsObjectBody

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Flag specifying if the subscriber wants to receive updates for a Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:subscribeToStatusUpdates

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Company Identifier of the company the subscriber wants to subscribe to (delegation scenario).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:subscribedTo

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The Logistics Object type to which the subscriber wants subscribe to
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subscription:topic

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Link to the initial version of the Logistics Object
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: timemap:original

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Link to the time gate of the Logistics Object, if applicable
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: timemap:timegate

owl:Class.rdfs:label: CompanyInformation

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Create model for the audit trail
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Create

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Memento entry from the time map

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Notification

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Operation Request contained in the PATCH body
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Operation

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Object to modify in the PATCH request
owl:Class.rdfs:label: OperationObject

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: PATCH Request body containing updates on a Logistics Object
owl:Class.rdfs:label: PatchRequest

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Subscription information sent to the publisher
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Subscription

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Timemap
